    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "UNITED AIRLINES CARGO\nEFFECTIVE JAN. 9,1979\nIR CARGO\nAIR CARGO AIR GI\nAIR CARGO AIRC\nAIR CARGO AR\nAIR CARGO AIR\nAIR CARGO\nAIR CARGO\nGO AIR CARGO\nGO AIR CARGO\nRGO AIR CARGO\nRGO AIR CARGO\nARGO AIR CARGO\nARGO AIR CARGI\nO MIRCORG\nCORO",
      "HONOLULU TIME\nPACIFIC TIME\nMOUNTAIN TIME\nL\nCENTRAL TIME\nEASTERN TIME\nTORONTO\nSEATTLE-TACOMA\nPORTLAND\nCHICAGO\nDETROIT CLEVELAND\nBOSTON\nHARTPORD-SPRINGFIELD\nNEW YORK-NEWARK\nPHILADELPHIA\nALTIMORE-WASHINGTON\nSAN FRANCISCO-OAKLAND\nSAN JOSE\nDENVER\nLAS VEGAS\nHONOLULU\nOS ANGELES\nSAN DIEGO\nHILO\nOnly cities having jet freighter or\nwide-body (B-747 and DC-10) service\nare represented. Standard route lines\nhave been replaced by indications of\ngeneral traffic flows on United Airlines,\n- Truck connections to\nwidebody hubs available\n(For example Buffalo/\nRochester to Cleveland) -\nFor complete information\ncall your local Air Freight\noffice."
